# Factory CLI / Droid: paths to exclude from AI agent context.
#
# `mirror/patches/` contains OSS public-mirror substitution artifacts used by
# `mirror/transform.ts` at mirror-CI time. Internal-dev agents must NOT read
# these as if they were canonical — canonical files live on `dev` outside this
# path.
#
# Reading substitution material as canonical would cause an agent to:
#   - Generate OSS-shaped output for internal-facing work
#   - Lose internal-team context from the real AGENTS.md / README.md / CHANGELOG.md
#   - Misinterpret patch-diff text as source-of-truth content
#
# See: mirror/AGENTS.md
mirror/patches/**
